com.nokia.maps.routing

Class Mode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.maps.routing.Mode

  • public class Mode
extends java.lang.Object
    The Mode encapsulates the parameters for one route calculation. Routing type must be one of the RoutingType constants. Transport mode array elements must be one of the TransportMode constants. Routing options array elements must be one of the RouteFeature constants.
    See Also:
    RoutingType, TransportMode, RouteFeature, TrafficMode
